  TaN Koan-im si7 sim2-mih8 lang5? I e5 tai7-chi3 ham3-ham3; chiau3 lang5 sou2 kong2 i si7 ¡§Pi2-khoat kok Biau7 Chong5 ong5 e5 te7 saN cha-bou2 kiaN2, mia5 Biau7-sian7. In lau7-pe7 seN3 Pou5 mia5 Ka, lau7-bo2 seN3 Pek-ga5 mia5 Po2; long2 bo5 hau7-seN, chi2 u7 saN e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2. Biau7-sian7 m7 ke3, thau chau2 khi3 siu heng7; in lau7-pe7 tiau3 i, i long2 m7 to3-khi3. In pe7 chiu7 toa7 siu7-khi3, chek-si5 chhe peng pang3-hoe2 sio i sou2 toa3 e5 sou2-chai7. Biau7-sian7 khoaN3-kiN3 hoe2 iam7-iam7, chiu7 kiu5 sin5-beng5 po2-pi3; au7-lai5 eng7 tek chhe chhak8 chhui3-chih8 hou7 i lau5 hoeh, chiu7 tui3 khong-tiong bu7 khi3, chek-si5-kan piN3 cho3 toa7 ang5-hou7, ak-hoa moa2-si7 e5 iam7-hoe2, pun2-sin bo5 sio--si2. In pe7 thiaN-tioh8 an2-ni it-hoat siu7-khi3, hoan-hu3 chiong Biau7-sian7 liah8-khi3 hoat-tiuN5 thai5. Tu2-a2 beh thai5 e5 si5 u7 ang5 e5 ho5-kong lai5 kham3, to-kiam3 soa3 chih8--khi3 thai5 be7 si2; jian5-au7 nng7 e5 tai7-chiong3 eng7 keng-hian5 soh ka7 i ka2-si2.¡¨ Au7-lai5 i chiu7 kau3 im-kan. Giam5-lo5 ong5 chun2 i hoe5 hun5 lai5 iong5-kan; tu2-tioh8 Sek-kia hut8 chiah chhoa7 i khi3 Oat8-kok lam5-hai2 Phou2-to5-san siu-heng7. Hit-si5 tu2-tioh8 Biau7 Chong5 ong5 tioh8 peN7. Biau7-sian7 chiaN3 hoa3 cho3 sian ka7 i i-ti7, liam5-piN chiu7 ho2, chiaN3 koh sio-jin7 cho3 pe7 kiaN2. 
  Au7-lai5 kam2-hoa3 choan5 ke khi3 Hiong-san siu heng7. Giok8-hong5 chiu7 hong Biau7-sian7 ho7-cho3 ¡§toa7 chu5-pi kiu3 khou2 Koan-im Phou5-sat¡¨. 
  Iau3 u7 pat8 lang5 kong2 pat8 khoan2. Ki5-sit8 si7 long2 bo5 iaN2 liau2-liau2. Ki5-sit8 Koan-im pun2-jian5 si7 cha-pou lang5; u7 lang5 kong2 si7 Sek-kia Bou5-ni5 e5 hak8-seng, kaN2 si7 Sek-kia Bou5-ni5 pun2-sin. 
  TaN chit e5 Sek-kia Bou5-ni5 si7 sim2-mih8 lang5? I si7 In3-tou7 kok lang5. Chit e5 In3-tou7 a2-si7 Thian-tek, si7 Tiong-kok sai lam5 peng5 e5 kok. Hit-tiat8 i chhut-si3, chiu7-si7 Chiu-tiau5 e5 si5-chun7, kui2-na7 kok u7 chhut seng3-jin5; Tiong kok chhut Khong2-chu2, Hi-li7-ni5 kok chhut Sok-la-te7, In3-tou7 kok chhut Sek-kia. Lan2 kong2 In3-tou7 kok m7-ku2 In3-tou7 si7 chong2 te7 ho7, pau-ham5 chin che7 kok, chiong5-tiong u7 chit8 e5 kok lang5 kong2 Ka-i5-oe7 kok, na7 si7 hit peng5 e5 lang5 kio3 i Benares, chiu7-si7 Tai5-oan5 5 hun7 1 hun7 e5 toa7 na7-tiaN7. Sek-kia Bou5-ni5 e5 lau7-pe7 cho3 hit e5 kok e5 ong5. Chiau3 lang5 sou2 liu5-thoan5 Sek-kia Bou5-ni5, chiu7-si7 thai3-chu2. Chhut mng5 ti7 ke-lou7 khoaN3 chit8 lang5 phoa3-peN7; cheng5 m7 bat khoaN3 phoa3-peN7 lang5 chiu7 khoaN3 liau2 be7 hiau2-tit, mng7 lou5-chai5 si7 an2-chaiN2-iuN7. Lou5-chai5 ke2-beng5, soa3 kong2 che si7 chha-put-to tak8 lang5 sou2 tioh8 keng-koe3 e5 su7. Thai3-chu2 thiaN liau2 hoan5-lo2. Bin5-a2-chai3 koh chhut-mng5, khoaN3 lang5 thau5 mng5 peh8-peh8 tuh koaiN2-a2 chin kan-khou2. Lou5-chai5 ka7 i kong2 si7 lau7 e5 ian5-kou3. Au7--jit8 koh chhut mng5 khoaN3 lang5 teh kng sin-si, iah8 m7 chai si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3. Lou5-chai5 kong2 si2 e5 i3-su3, tak8 lang5 tioh8 keng-koe3.
  Sek-kia Bou5-ni5 thiaN liau2 na2 kan-khou2, chiu7 tiaN7-tioh8 m7-ai3 toa3 ti7 ong5-kiong lai7, iah8 m7 kaN2 kap i e5 bou2 kiaN2 saN si5, thau chau2 khi3 bih ti7 chhiu7-na5 lai7 teh un2-ku, khoaN3 u7 sim2-mih8 hoat-tou7 thang thoat-li7 se3-kan e5 kan-khou2. Koe3 kui2-na7 ni5 chiu7 siuN7 tioh8 chit8 teng2-ho7 e5 hoat-tou7, chiu7-si7 tioh8 choat8 hit e5 ¡§ai3-iok8¡¨, hou7 hit e5 ai3-iok8 e7 thang chhin-chhiuN7 hoe2 hoa-khi3; lang5 tioh8 m7-ai3 chiN5, m7-ai3 mia5-siaN, m7-ai3 khoaN3-oah8, tak8 hang7 tioh8 m7-ai3 lang5 e5 kan-khou2 long2 si7 tui3 hit e5 ai3-iok8 siN-khi2; na7 long2 m7-ai3 sim2-mih8 chiu7 u7 bian2 kan-khou2. 
  I2-keng kau3 saN chap8 hoe3 chiu7 chio hak8-seng; hak8-seng na2 che7. Kau3 80 hoe3 i chiu7 si2. Si2 liau2-au7 i e5 hak8-seng chiu7 thoan5 i e5 kau3, m7-na7 ti7 In3-tou7 kok thoan5, soa3 thoan5 kau3 Tiong-kok. Kau3 Han3 Beng5-te3 e5 si5 chiu7 Tiong-kok u7 seng5-siu7 put8 kau3 e5 to7-li2. M7-ku2 na2 thoan5 na2 sia5-khi3; Sek-kia Bou5-ni5 long2 bo5 kio3-lang5 tioh8 jin7 i cho3 sin5-beng5, iah8 long2 bo5 kio3 lang5 tioh8 chhai7 sim2-mih8 Koan-e5 siong7, a2-si7 pat8 mih8 e5 siong7, kan-ta kio3 lang5 tioh8 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 pun5 hoa hit-e5 ¡§ai3-iok8¡¨ e5 hoe2, khoaN3-phoa3 se3-kan e5 hok-khi3. 
  Lang5 i2-keng khi3 hok8-sai7 goa7 kok put8, chiu7-si7 Sek-kia, Koan-im, be7 bian2-tit tioh8 siuN7 kong2, Hok8-sai7 pun2-te7 put8 iau2 khah ho2. Sou2-i2 To7 kau3 e5 lang5, in-ui7 m7-ai3 khah su Sek kau3, khng3 hong5-te3 tioh8 thek-hong pun2-te7 lang5. Si7 tui3 an2-ni chiu7 Giok8-hong5 siong7-te3 hou7 lang5 keng3-pai3. Giok8-hong5 siong7-te3 si7 Han3-tiau5 boe2 chhut-si3 e5 lang5. I seN3 TiuN, mia5 Gi5. I e5 lau7-pe7 si7 TiuN Lou2, eng7 oe7-hu5 e5 kang than3 chiN5. Chiau3 lang5 kong2, chit e5 TiuN Gi5 cho3 chin7-tiong e5 jin5-sin5 ti7 kok-ka iah8 si7 iau3-kin2 To7 kau3. Au7-lai5 i si2 liau2-au7 chiu7 Song3 Chin-chong hou7 To7 kau3 e5 lang5 in2-iu2 lai5 thek-hong i cho3 Giok8-hong5 Tai7 te3. Koh Song3 Hui-chong ka7 i thek-hong cho3 Giok8-hong5 siong7-te3. Na7-si7 hong Giok8-hong5 liau2-au7, bo5 loa7 ku2, Hui-chong kap i e5 ke-koan3 long2 hou7 Kim-kok lang5 liah8 khi3, siu7 che7-che7 leng5-jiok8, soa3 si2 ti7 Ngou2-kok siaN5.
  Chiau3 an2-ni khoaN3 chheng goa7 ni5 long2 bo5 chit8 e5 giok8-hong5 siong7-te3. Hit si5 sim2-mih8 lang5 teh koan2 thiN te7 ? Sit8-chai7 si7 hong5-te3 chho3-gou7 hong, iah8 peh-siN3 chho3-gou7 hok8-sai7. 
  Ma2-chou2 si7 sim2-mih8 lang5? Khiok lang5 kong2 kui2-na7 khoan2; khah siong5 kong2 i siok8 ti7 Hok-kian3 seng2 e5 Hin-hoa3 hu2. I e5 pe7 siN3 Lim5, i e5 lau7-bu2 siN3 Tan5. I pun2-sin kio3 cho3 Bek8, chhut-si3 ti7 Tong5-tiau5 Hian5-chong e5 si5. ¡§I e5 hiaN-ti7 si3 lang5 u7 ti7 hai2 goa7 cho3 seng-li2; u7 chit8 jit8 Bek8-a2 kha chhiu2 liau-liau--khi3, bak8-chiu be7 tng2-lun5; i e5 pe7 bu2 liah8-chun2 tioh8 soa chiu7 kin2-kin2 kio3 i chheN2. Chit8 e7 chheN2 Bek8-a2 chiu7 ka7 in pe7 bu2 kong2, ¡§Thai3 m7 hou7 goa2 kiu3 goa2 e5 hiaN-ti7 leh?¡¨ In pe7 bu2 be7 hiau2-tit. Theng5 nng7 saN jit8 ku2 i e5 hiaN-ti7 chiu7 thi5-khau3 to3-lai5, kong2 in cheng5 jit8 tu2-tioh8 toa7 hong, u7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 khan phang5 lai5 teh chhoa7 in hiaN-ti7 si3 lang5 bo5 siang7 chun5, toa7-hiaN hou7 eng2 kham3-si2, chun5 long2 hoai7-khi3. In pe7 bu2 chiaN3 chai cheng5 jit8 Bek8-a2 sit-khi3 si7 khi3 kiu3 in hiaN-ti7, toa7-hiaN si2 khi3, si7 in-ui7 siuN kin2 kio3 i chheN2 chiaN3 kiu3 be7 hu3. Tui3 an2-ni chhu3-piN chiu7 lam7-sam2 kong2 chit e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 tek-to7, e7 kiu3 chun5-chiah tu2-tioh8 hong-eng2 e5 gui5-hiam2. Kau3 Song3 Sian7-chong chiu7 thek-hong Lim5 Bek8 cho3 Leng5-hui7 hu-jin5. Beng5 Eng2-lok8 hong i cho3 Po2-hou7 kok ti3-im3 peh-siN3 e5 Thian-hui. 
