  M7-ku2 bo5 tek-khak tioh8 eng7 Sin5-chu2 lai5 keng3 lan2 e5 si7-toa7 lang5. Khah cha2 si7 eng7 si-chu2, chiu7-si7 lang5 si2 liau2 chiu7 ¡§kau3 hian3-che3 e5 si5 u7 eng7 i e5 toa7-sun chng cho3 chou2-chong e5 si-siong7 chiaN3-chiaN3 teh che7, hou7 tang5-chok8 e5 lang5 pai5 che3-mih8 hian3-che3 kui7-pai3, piau2-beng5 hau3-keng3 e5 i3-su3¡¨. Hit-tiap8 iau2-boe7 u7 eng7 bok8-chu2. Chiau3 lang5 liu5-thoan5 si7 Teng-lan5 siat bok8-chu2. Teng-lan5 si7 chin put-hau3 e5 kiaN2 pek-si2 i e5 lau7-bu2. Lan2 na7 oh8 Gou5 Beng2 chhi7 bang2, a2-si7 oh8 Beng7 Chong khok-tek si7 khah-ho2. Lun7 hiah-e5 piN2 pang-a2 si7 chit8 chhioh koan5 na7-tiaN7, lan2 e5 kong-ma2 tiam3 hia thai2 e7 loh8? Koh lan2 tioh8 siuN7, lan2 e5 pe7-bo2 na7 si2, lan2 7 jit8 ku2 chit8 jit8 hau3 2 tng3; ke3 khi3 chhe it chap8 gou7 na7-tiaN7; tui3 ni5 i2-au7 hau3 ni5 cheh, chiaN3 bian2-ki7. Lan2 tak8-jit8 chiah8 saN-tng3; iah8 lan2 e5 kong-ma2 chit8 ni5 e5 tiong-kan chiah8 bo5 kui2 tng3. I iah8 bo5 lai5-chiah8; i na7 lai5 chiah8 lan2 chiu7 m7-kaN2 hau3. Ki5-sit8 si7 lan2 beh hau3 ka-ti7 e5 pak-tou2 na7-tiaN7, long2 bo5 teh siuN7 lan2 e5 kong-ma2 ai3 chiah8 sim2-mih8 hoe3, kan-ta teh siuN7 lan2 ka-ti7 ai3 chiah8 sim2-mih8. Kau3 cho3 ki7 e5 jit8 kau3, lan2 tioh8 hoan5-lo2 siuN7 kong2. TaN goa2 e5 si7-toa7 lang5 sng2-khi3, kin-a2-jit8 bo5 thang saN-kiN3. Kho2-sioh lang5 bo5 siuN7 chit e5 i3-su3; u7-si5 gin2-na2 na7 hau2, lau7-bo2 ka7 i kong2, ¡§EN-a2 tiam7-tiam7, lan2 koh nng7 saN jit8 beh cho3 ki7 thang chiah8¡¨. 
  Sit8-chai7 sin5 bo5 thang lai5 chiah8; na7 i2-keng kau3 im-kan chiu7 bo5 thang koh lai5. Iah8 sui-jian5 lai5, sin5 iu5-goan5 bo5 ai3 chiah8. U7-si5 lang5 kong2, Goa2 chai iaN2; put-ko3 si7 ai3 hau3 chit8 tiam2 sim, koe3 sim hau3 na7-tiaN7. Sit8-chai7 na7 beh an2-ni, chiu7 u7 pat8 mih8 e5 hoat-tou7; lan2 thang hip chit8 e5 siong7, a2-si7 chhau chit8 e5 chok8-phou2 lai5 ki3-liam7. Siong7-te3 it iau3-kin2 si7 lan2 chai7-siN tioh8 sun7 i; iah8 si2 au7 tioh8 chiau3 i e5 ka3-si7. Siok8-gu2 kong2:--¡§Chai7 siN chiah8 chit8 liap8 tau7, khah ho2 si2 liau2 chiah8 chit8-e5 ti-thau5¡¨; iah8 ¡§Chai7 siN bo5 thang che3 au5, si2 liau2 che3 koaN-chha5-thau5¡¨. 
